- check for the required dependencies
- check if it has a .gitignore file
- check if a components folder exists
- check if the app has not been created using 'webpack' or 'Create React App', and strictly use Vite
- check if Vitest has been used rather than Jest
- check to avoid using implict Any in typescript
- check to avoid using React.FC
- check to avoid using Redux, and use Zustand instead
- check if readme is descriptive
- check if prettier config exists
- check if functions contain documentation